snippet.title: The Last Campfire First Look Gameplay
snippet.description:
Lead Designer on The Last Campfire, Steven Burgess, sat down with Inside Xbox to take them through an exclusive first look of gameplay.

Coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch and PC, Summer 2020.

www.thelastcampfiregame.com
